Gibberize
==========

This crabgrass mod allow add a translation user interface to crabgrass.

Usage
=======

edit config/routes.rb
  map.from_plugin :gibberize

Specify the logins you want to be translators in config/sites.yml:

<begin>
default:
  name: crabgrass
  domain: localhost
  email_sender: 'crabgrass-system@localhost'
  secret: 'd24833cab5fafcd17f2c555f7663c0524a938e5ed6df2af8bf134d3959fc8ac3214fa8c7'
  pagination_size: 29
  translators:
  - sally
  - bob
<end>

Uncomment gibberize on config/mods_enabled.list

Run Gibberize Migrations:

$ ./script/generate plugin_migration
$ rake db:migrate

In development mode you may want to load Gibberize fixtures:
$ rake db:fixtures:plugins:load

restart rails and browse to: http://localhost:3000/gibberize

Credits
=======

The Gibberize mod is based on Gibberize <http://code.autistici.org/project/gibberize>
and the SuperAdmin mod.
Turned into a mod by Pietro Ferrari <pietro@riseup.net>

